
IF YOU OWN THE FULL GAME AND WISH TO USE THIS TRACK
---------------------------------------------------

Floppy Users
------------

1 - Ensure this disk is named XTR4. To do this use select the disk icon in
    Workbench, then select 'Rename' from the 'Icons' menu.

2 - From the game select play single track, and insert this disk into the drive.



HD Users
--------

Copy the following directories to the directory in which XTR was installed :

Backgrounds
Tiles
Tracks
Objects
Worlds
Layouts

When the game is next booted, select play single track and you will find this
track is now available.

